{"tid":1097393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台女掃墓後眼腫發炎　檢查發現左眼有4隻活汗蜂","createTime":"2019-04-08T10:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T13:46:41.000Z","uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"282499e98d723aea86741d1818dd95c9c4b2054e","tid":1097393,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"高雄市一名何姓女子上周六（3月30日）上山掃墓時遇到風沙入眼，經沖洗後卻未見好轉，反而紅腫熱痛。她在就醫後才驚悉，原來自己左眼眼皮底下藏了4隻奄奄一息的「汗蜂」，造成角膜出現損傷糜爛，差點失明。<br />\n<br />\n汗蜂學名為Halictidae，屬於「膜翅目集蜂科」蜂類，喜歡接近汗水、淚水。收治病例的輔英科技大學附設醫院眼科教授洪啓庭周四（4日）表示，汗蜂入眼是全球首宗。<br />\n<br />\n慎入:<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2641178/org/a870cc894204b3bf076cd4af73f7b3e6.png/FYCi689ODLrP7iB3bvlCWh9XMJkskO6kitNSfIrTUnw?v=w1280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2641178%2Forg%2Fa870cc894204b3bf076cd4af73f7b3e6.png%2FFYCi689ODLrP7iB3bvlCWh9XMJkskO6kitNSfIrTUnw%3Fv%3Dw1280&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=b3aaa00e\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2641178/org/a870cc894204b3bf076cd4af73f7b3e6.png/FYCi689ODLrP7iB3bvlCWh9XMJkskO6kitNSfIrTUnw?v=w1280</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2641182/org/838e0831a7a781ecabe6b77bdd53ae3c.jpg/rkno9uUPOVOmeh59zpvK86_xubNm53FAFy0W5RctFuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2641182%2Forg%2F838e0831a7a781ecabe6b77bdd53ae3c.jpg%2Frkno9uUPOVOmeh59zpvK86_xubNm53FAFy0W5RctFuU&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=76e96b6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2641182/org/838e0831a7a781ecabe6b77bdd53ae3c.jpg/rkno9uUPOVOmeh59zpvK86_xubNm53FAFy0W5RctFuU</a><br />\n<br />\n據眼科教授洪啓庭介紹，何小姐到院時左眼已腫如鹹蛋般大小，初步觀察有蜂窩性組織炎的現象，先冰敷减緩腫脹，再輔以光學顯微鏡用細棉棒探入眼皮，發現4隻3毫米大小的汗蜂吸附在眼球上，因此小心翼翼在不破壞蟲體的情况下一隻隻取出。<br />\n<br />\n他還說，蜂類在何小姐的眼球上移動，加上蟲體表面物質，造成結膜合並角膜的大片糜爛，導致視力剩下0.1；所幸她未揉眼，這些汗蜂也未攻擊眼球組織，否則蜂類體內的複雜組織，很有可能造成腦炎、中樞神經發炎成爲植物人，還要摘去眼球等嚴重後果。何小姐經3天治療後，視力已恢復到0.8。<br />\n<br />\n洪啓庭還稱，經過翻查文獻，確認這是世界首例，將投稿相關期刊。他又提醒，在郊外活動時，若有異物入侵眼睛，應緊記不要大力揉眼，有需要應立刻求醫，配戴太陽眼鏡亦可以阻隔昆蟲以至蜂類的襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/314731/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E6%8E%83%E5%A2%93%E5%BE%8C%E7%9C%BC%E8%85%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%82%8E-%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%A6%E7%9C%BC%E6%9C%894%E9%9A%BB%E6%B4%BB%E6%B1%97%E8%9C%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F314731%2F%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258E%2583%25E5%25A2%2593%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259C%25BC%25E8%2585%25AB%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E7%259C%25BC%25E6%259C%25894%25E9%259A%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%25B1%2597%25E8%259C%2582&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfp7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=49218792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/314731/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8F%B0%E5%A5%B3%E6%8E%83%E5%A2%93%E5%BE%8C%E7%9C%BC%E8%85%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%82%8E-%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%A6%E7%9C%BC%E6%9C%894%E9%9A%BB%E6%B4%BB%E6%B1%97%E8%9C%82</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都入到去隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcb0a97afbcaa0f9ff087141b817c132ad15fb9","tid":1097393,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"新聞唔擺圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKWFpdJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKWFpdJ.jpg&h=24d28919&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cda2a66b6d59d256922f88490d52c78e99e8df3"